<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Your Trial Has Ended - Origin Food House</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: #9E9E9E; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="margin: 0;">Your Trial Has Ended</h1>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 30px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-top: none; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;">
    <p>Hi {{ownerName}},</p>

    <p>Your 30-day Standard tier trial for <strong>{{storeName}}</strong> has ended.</p>

    <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Account Status:</h3>
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Previous Tier:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-decoration: line-through;">Standard (Trial)</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Current Tier:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #2196F3; font-weight: bold;">Free</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Downgraded On:</strong></td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{downgradedAt}}</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Your Free tier now includes:</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>✅ Up to 3 tables</li>
      <li>✅ Up to 20 menu items</li>
      <li>✅ 1 staff account</li>
      <li>✅ Up to 100 orders per month</li>
      <li>✅ Basic features</li>
    </ul>

    <div style="background: #fff3cd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        <strong>Note:</strong> If you exceeded Free tier limits during your trial, some features may be restricted until you upgrade or reduce usage.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p><strong>Want to continue with full features?</strong></p>
    <p>Upgrade to Standard or Premium to unlock all the features you had during your trial:</p>

    <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 12px; border: 2px solid #4CAF50; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center;">
            <strong style="font-size: 18px; color: #4CAF50;">Standard</strong><br>
            <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">$240</span>/year<br>
            <span style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">10 tables • 100 items • 5 staff</span>
          </td>
          <td style="width: 20px;"></td>
          <td style="padding: 12px; border: 2px solid #FFD700; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center;">
            <strong style="font-size: 18px; color: #FF9800;">Premium</strong><br>
            <span style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">$1200</span>/year<br>
            <span style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">Unlimited everything + priority support</span>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{upgradeUrl}}" style="background: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">
        Upgrade Now
      </a>
    </p>

    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
      Thank you for trying Origin Food House! We hope you had a great experience.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #f5f5f5; padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px;">
    &copy; {{year}} Origin Food House. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</body>
</html>
